## Key Takeaways

1. The Strategic Rationale
AI models prioritize platforms with high "structural trust." To improve your brand’s AI visibility, you must shift focus toward the specific high-authority ecosystems where AI systems are most likely to source their answers.

2. The Big Six Platforms
The strategy identifies six critical channels: YouTube, LinkedIn, Reddit, Quora, Medium, and Google Business Profile. These are prioritized because of their massive datasets, high domain authority, and direct integration with major AI players like Google and Microsoft.

3. Execution Approach
Don't spread yourself thin. Select the platform that best fits your expertise and establish a consistent, long-term publishing cadence. This builds a compounding effect, positioning your content as a credible, recurring citation in AI-generated responses.

